- OW Module Forms 1.0.0 extension information

About OW Module Forms
=====================

A set of skeleton classes to build easily forms in a module/view way.

It allows to build forms with all standard input types (texts, textareas, radiobuttons,
selects, checkboxes ...) and bind them validators. These validators work with jquery
to make an instant validation and a submit validation.

Technical information
=====================

    OW Module Forms uses:
    - jQuery                            http://www.jquery.com
    - PHP
    - eZjscore extension

Installation
============

See doc/INSTALL.txt

